  "abstract": "<p>PacBio Sequence data associated with genetic stock KDH13.Datasets include genome resources and annotated files associated with the manuscript \"Long-read genome assembly of Double Haploid Sugar Beet KDH13 provides roadmap for durable genetic resistance to Beet Curly Top Virus\". This includes genome assembly, ordered genome assembly, protein predictions, variant call format files for an F1 hybrid (KDH13xKDH19-17).</p>\r\n",
