    }
  ],
  "keywords": [
    "Genomics"
  ],
  "methods": "<p>Detailed information such as code is stored within the github repo <a href=\"https://github.com/BetaGenomeNinja/PacBio_KDH13\">https://github.com/BetaGenomeNinja/PacBio_KDH13</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Detailed methods are documented in the publication \"Long-read genome assembly of Double Haploid Sugar Beet KDH13 provides roadmap for durable genetic resistance to Beet Curly Top Virus\".</p>\r\n",
